title: Child rapper says she and brother are alive after Instagram statement said they had both died
description: A 14-year-old rapper and social media star who was reported to have died has said she is in fact safe and alive.

title: FIFA urged by UN to keep World Cup equal prize money promise
description: FIFA should ensure there is equal prize money by the next Women's World Cup, the United Nations agency for women's rights has told Sky News.

title: Joe Biden declares Hawaii 'major disaster' after devastating wildfires
description: Joe Biden has declared Hawaii a disaster area, clearing the way for federal aid to help Maui residents and businesses recover from devastating wildfires.

title: 'Most exciting day of my life': Virgin Galactic tourists react after flight to edge of space
description: Virgin Galactic has taken its first tourists to the edge of space, with an 80-year-old British ex-Olympian saying the trip "exceeded my wildest dreams".

title: Barbie movie banned in Kuwait as Lebanon also moves to censor film
description: Kuwait has banned the film Barbie in a bid to protect "public ethics and social traditions," while a Lebanese minister has made moves to censor the film on grounds it "promotes homosexuality and sexual transformation".

title: Punishment for owning an LGBT watch revealed by Malaysia
description: Malaysia's government says it is banning all Swatch products that contain lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender or queer elements.

title: How worried should we be about new COVID variant described as 'one to watch'?
description: A new sub-lineage of the Omicron COVID variant now makes up one in seven cases in the UK.

title: Sick cats in Cyprus begin COVID drug treatment
description: Cats in Cyprus are being given human COVID-19 medicine in an effort to slow the spread of a feline mutation of the virus that has left thousands of animals dead on the island.

title: Hawaii wildfires in pictures: Images show devastation on island of Maui
description: These images show the devastation wreaked by wildfires in the historic Hawaiian town of Lahaina.

title: New COVID strain spreading across UK designated 'variant of interest' by WHO
description: A new fast-spreading COVID strain has been designated a "variant of interest" by the World Health Organisation.

title: Ecuadorian presidential candidate Fernando Villavicencio shot dead at political rally
description: Ecuadorian presidential candidate Fernando Villavicencio has been shot and killed by an unidentified gunman while at a political rally in Quito.
